short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension add some new functions to Fastcup.net. Automatic match acceptance and more.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The extension allows you to enable automatic acceptance of a match in matchmaking mode and in custom matches mode, remember the selected regions to search for a match.
